@node Main "Pivoto - Documentation"

                              'Pivoto' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Pivoto' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on a 7 by 7 tiles board, in
which your goal is to remove all the 'front facing' (facing toward
you) coloured tiles by aligning them with adjacent tiles (either
horizontally or vertically) of the same colour. The more tiles of
the same colour that are next to each other, the more points you
make.

  Have fun!

